description:
Eau de Parfum 100ml
The oriental floral perfume Tom Ford Cafe Rose was created in 2012 for men and women. The basis of the Cafe Rose perfume composition is a bouquet of roses, complemented by a deep tonic coffee aroma. Tom Ford Cafe Rose is characterized by a delicious, exotic, seductive aroma. The Cafe Rose fragrance invites us to dive into the secret process of growing rare varieties of roses. This composition consists of three different types of rose essence, flavored with spices and dark coffee.
Top notes: Saffron, Black pepper, May rose;
Heart notes: Turkish rose, Bulgarian rose, coffee;
Base notes: Frankincense, Ambergris, Sandalwood, Patchouli.

50ML Eau de Toilette
Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette is a delicate and playful scent that truly feels like spring in a bottle and that embodies the Miss Dior spirit perfectly.
As its antecedents, the Dior Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette has a sophisticated flask that immediately reminds us of the couture luxurious spirit. Introduce this enchanting scent as your daily perfume, and complement its use with other products from the same range in order to enhance its fragrance trail.

Top notes: sicilian mandarin, calabrian bergamot;
Heart notes: pink peony, damask rose, apricot and peach;
Base notes: white musk.

50ML Eau de Parfum
Gucci Bloom Eau de Parfum is a scent that celebrates authenticity, vitality as well as the diversity of women — flourishing in a natural, expressive and individual way. Blended by master perfumer Alberto Morillas under the direction of the House’s Creative Director, Gucci Bloom is created to unfold like its name, capturing the rich scent of a thriving garden filled with an abundance of flowers. Tuberose and jasmine coupled with Rangoon Creeper — a unique flower from South India that is for the first time in perfumery to create a rich fragrance that transports the wearer to an imaginary garden.

Top notes: jasmine;
Heart notes: tuberose;
Base notes: rangoon creeper.
